  "texts": [
    "This leads to all test instances from a given class having near identical top-k influence rankings.",
    "RPS-LJE's alternate definition of i is less influenced by a training instance's loss value, which enables RPS-LJE to generate more semantically meaningful influence rankings.",
    "Extending representer point to other regularizers Yeh et al.'s (2018) representer point formulation exclusively considers L 2 -regularized models.",
    "Intuitively, regulari- zation's role is to encourage the model parameters to meet certain desired properties, which may necessitate the use of alternate regularizers.",
    "For example, L 1 regularization is often used to induce sparse minimizers."
